platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Discover the wonders of the universe with this powerful, easy-to-use astronomy toolkit. Just aim your device to view the real-time positions of planets, stars, constellations, and more in a stunning interactive map. Zoom in to explore Wikipedia articles, 3D models, and other media related to your favorite celestial bodies.
这一简单易用、功能强大的天文观星工具让你尽情探索宇宙奥秘。只需将手中的设备对准夜空, 便可观测到行星、恒星及万千星座的实时方位, 互动星图更是令人叹为观止。放大画面还可以查看 3D 模型以及其它相关天体资讯。
